# Test API Endpoints

## 1. Health Check
GET http://localhost:5000/api/health

## 2. Register New User
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "Test User",
  "email": "test@example.com",
  "password": "testpassword123"
}

## 3. Login
POST http://localhost:5000/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "admin@enernova.id",
  "password": "admin123"
}

## 4. Get All Journals (No Auth Required)
GET http://localhost:5000/api/journals

## 5. Get All Journals with Filter
GET http://localhost:5000/api/journals?status=APPROVED&search=solar

## 6. Get Single Journal
GET http://localhost:5000/api/journals/:id

## 7. Create New Journal (Auth Required)
POST http://localhost:5000/api/journals
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "filename": "new-journal.pdf",
  "title": "Test Journal",
  "detectedAuthor": "Test Author",
  "authorInstitution": "Test University",
  "publicationYear": "2024",
  "journalSource": "Test Source",
  "doi": "10.1234/test.2024",
  "pdfUrl": "/data_jurnal/new-journal.pdf",
  "fileSize": "1.5 MB",
  "contentPreview": "This is a test journal..."
}

## 8. Update Journal Status (Admin Only)
PATCH http://localhost:5000/api/journals/:id/status
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "APPROVED"
}

## 9. Delete Journal (Admin Only)
DELETE http://localhost:5000/api/journals/:id
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE

## 10. Chat with AI
POST http://localhost:5000/api/chat
Authorization: Bearer YOUR_TOKEN_HERE
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Apa itu energi terbarukan?"
}
